{{>layout/header}}

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .announce-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background-color: #LightYellow;
        border: 1px solid #ddd; /* 테두리 추가 */
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .announce-header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #LightYellow;
        padding: 20px;
        border-top-left-radius: 8px;
        border-top-right-radius: 8px;
    }

    .announce-content {
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .announce-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #007bff;
    }

    .announce-description {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold; /* 굵은 글꼴 추가 */
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
    }

    .announce-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .announce-button:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
    }
</style>

<body>

<div class="announce-container">
    <div class="announce-header">
        <h1>공지 사항</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="announce-content">
        <div class="announce-title"> * HOW TO SAVE OUR EARTH *</div>
        <div class="announce-description">


            <p>
                1. **Reduce, Reuse, Recycle:**<br>
                - Minimize waste by reducing consumption.<br>
                - Reuse items whenever possible.<br>
                - Recycle materials like paper, glass, and plastic.</p>

            <p>
                2. **Conserve Water:**<br>
                - Fix leaks promptly.<br>
                - Use water-efficient appliances.<br>
                - Turn off taps when not in use.</p>
            <p>
                3. **Save Energy:**<br>
                - Use energy-efficient appliances and light bulbs.<br>
                - Turn off lights and electronics when not needed.<br>
                - Consider renewable energy sources.</p>
            <p>
                4. **Plant Trees:**<br>
                - Trees absorb carbon dioxide and provide oxygen.<br>
                - Participate in tree-planting initiatives.</p>
            <p>
                5. **Choose Sustainable Products:**<br>
                - Support eco-friendly and sustainable products.<br>
                - Avoid single-use plastics.</p>
            <p>
                6. **Carpool and Use Public Transportation:**<br>
                - Reduce carbon emissions by sharing rides.<br>
                - Opt for public transportation to lessen traffic.</p>
            <p>
                7. **Educate Others:**<br>
                - Spread awareness about environmental issues.<br>
                - Encourage others to adopt eco-friendly practices.</p><br>

            Remember, small actions can collectively make a big difference in preserving our planet.
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="announce-button">Learn More</a>
    </div>
</div>

{{>layout/footer}}

